                                Format

        You can format a disk by selecting the disk icon, holding down
Shift, then double-clicking on the Format icon. The formatting procedure
will follow the same steps as if you had chosen the Format Disk from the
pull down menus.

        The Format program is used by the Format Disk menu item in the Icon
menu. If you simply double on the Format icon, you will be referred to the
Format Disk menu item.


